      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see what you mean about the specific accounts, but what about when you have a lot of different little tasks running all at once? sometimes it feels like things are getting messy or \"uncontrolled\" when you have too many different permissions flying around. how do you keep everything organized so it doesn't turn into chaos?",
